    <p>In­dulge in a week­end break­fast by the Ma­rina Bay wa­ter­front with Bread Street Kitchen’s re­vamped clas­sic English break­fast menu. Apart from favourites such as eggs Bene­dict royale and but­ter­milk pan­cakes, the restau­rant is also dish­ing out new of­fer­ings such as beef brisket sand­wich and smoked salmon bagel. Pair with a glass of BSK Blends – take your pick from six house­made smooth­ies.</p>
    <p>WHERE: Bread Street Kitchen by Gor­don Ram­say, L1-81, Bay Level, The Shoppes at Ma­rina Bay Sands, 2 Bayfront Av­enue MRT: Bayfront WHEN: Satur­day and Sun­day, 8.30am to 11am PRICE: Smoked salmon bagel, $19++ TEL: 6688-5665</p>
    <p>INFO: www.marin­abaysands.com/ restau­rants/bread-streetk­itchen.html</p>


